@NODE "Questions" "Les Questions-Réponses"
@TOC "MAIN"
@{b}@{u}6. Questions & answers@{ub}@{uu}

    @{b}Comment peut-on lancer BlitzBank avec un compte ouvert ?@{ub}

        You just have to double-click on account icon and BlitzBank will load and open
        this account automatically.

    @{b}How can I start BlitzBank with several opened accounts?@{ub}

      You just have to select all accounts icon that you want to see opened (click on each icon
      with SHIFT key pressed), then double-click on BlitzBank icon (still having SHIFT key down).
      You can also simplier double-click on an account icon, then after BlitzBank loading, double-
      click on other accounts icon. All accounts will be opened in the same BlitzBank thanks to a
      messages port gestion. (this method requires 550 Ko more because BlitzBank will be
      opened a second time for a while)

    @{b}Is it possible to create a negative borrowing operation ?@{ub}

        Yes! It is useful when you lend money and you are repayed with interests.

    @{b}How can I save iconification position ?@{ub}

        You must iconify BlitzBank, then place the iconification where you want,
        uniconify BlitzBank and then save preferences.

    @{b}Why BlitzBank does not always ask if we want to save an account ?@{ub}

        BlitzBank only displays a save request only for accounts that have been modified. If it
        asked you nothing, it means that your account has already been saved or that it hasn't
        been modified.

    @{b}Why is it possible to enter an operation with a null sum ?@{ub}

        With this possibility you can enter commentary lines in your account. You can for example
        put each month to the fore writting down "Month xxx..."  Those commentaries will have
        their own color you will be able to set in the@{"Preferences" LINK "préférences" 10}.
        No amount or category will be displyed for those lines.
        Since version 2.17, you don't need to enter the month anymore since it can be made
        automatically : "month %m" will indicate to the computer it will have to inscribe "month..."
        followed by the date's operation corresponding month. For example, if the operation
        appears at 01/09/96, "month %m" will display "september month". In fact, "%m" has been
        replaced by "September". See also @{"Operation nature" LINK "éditer" 19}.

    @{b}How can I help BlitzBank understand that the documentation has moved in another
        drawer ?@{ub}

        You have to edit Blitzbank icon tooltype "HELPDRAWER" writting down the drawer
        where the documentation is.
        Example:  HELPDRAWER=Help:

    @{b}Why BlitzBank sometimes does GURU ? @{ub}

        This is not a bug but only a memory problem. BlitzBank needs 1,6 Mb of memory to run
        correctly. If you don't have as much memory, you may get a crash. Moreover, take care
        to always have that amount free. When iconified, BlitzBank frees some memory, but it will
        need it back when uniconified. In short, if you have for example 4 Mb before starting
        BlitzBank, keep in mind that you should not use more than 2.4 Mb for other tasks. That
        way, you'll be sure not to have a crash.
        Moreover, music module takes memory. Like this, if you save preferences without the
        option 'play module', the needed memory will be free.
        If all those conditions are verified, you should rather contact the author.

    @{b}When several operations have the same date, how can I put one operation at the top of the list ? @{ub}

        You just have to click on operation date you want to see at the first place and choose "Ok".
        (it doesn't work with spreaded operations).

    @{b}The documentation does not appear when I press the 'HELP' key ? @{ub}

        Amigaguide documentation will only be displayed if you gave the correct complete path for
        Multiview or Amigaguide. To do this, click one time on Blitzbank.guide icon and select
        the tool 'information' from the 'icon' Workbench's menu. Enter then the complete path for
        Multiview (example: sys:utilities/multiview). Even if it works when you double-click on
        Blitzbank.guide icon, it's not sure that it will work in BLitzbank because it is necessary
        for it to know the COMPLETE path for the display tool.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "AuSujetDe" "Au Sujet De ..."
@TOC "MAIN"
@{b}@{u}1.Introduction
1.1 About BLitzbank@{ub}@{uu}

BlitzBank is a powerful bank and personal accounts gestion software. It allows by simply adding
operations to automatically update your account. With the help of powerful functions like
automatic deduction / payment, it can even write them at your place!
A personnaly used ABank and other bank accounts gestion software and noticed that I could
bring lots of improvements.
Just have a look :
   - day gestion, month and @{fg shine}YEAR@{fg text} . (you can go from 1978 to 2077 !!)

   - support of @{fg shine}" @{"cut copy paste" LINK "éditer" 51} "@{fg text}

   - windows, screens, cells, gadgets and totally system friendly menus (2.0+)

   - automatic sorting using date and detection of its validity using a perpetual calendar.

   - @{fg shine}Pie-charts @{"Statistics" LINK "Outils"}@{fg text} with precise filters,
     IFF format save and graphic printing.

   - @{"Print" LINK "Outils" 96} with ultra selective filter.

   - In addition of bank validated or not operations, portfolio gestion and by the way,
     @{fg shine}deposits and withdrawal cash gestion@{fg text}.

   - @{fg shine}Operations classification to category @{fg text} (some of them are predefined).

   - Lines display with ultra selective filter.

   - @{fg shine}@{"automatic deductions/deposits" LINK "Outils" 30} gestion@{fg text}
      including all necessary options.

   - @{fg shine}Bank or personal @{"loans" LINK "éditer" 34} gestion and follow up@{fg text},
     with repayment automatic calculation and transfer according to interest rates and borrowings
     duration.

   - Expenses and receipts expectation thanks to a @{fg shine}@{"budgetary forecast"
     LINK "Outils" 69}@{fg text}.

   - @{fg shine}@{"Transfers" LINK "éditer" 34}@{fg text} gestion (automatic or not)
     between several accounts.

   - @{fg shine}Recognition and reading of Abank file format.@{fg text}

   - Possibility to @{fg shine}@{"merge" LINK "Projet"} two accounts@{fg text}.

   - 'Secret' option to hide your sums safe from prying eyes.

   - Bank logos and account type gestion with possibility of@{"importation" LINK "Outils" 108}.

   - @{fg shine}@{"Password" LINK "éditer" 79}@{fg text} gestion.

   - @{"Search\replace" LINK "Recherche"} support.

   - @{"iconification" LINK "Projet" 24} possibility.

   - Reqtools files and screenmode requesters.

   - Use of ReqTools.library (requesters) and Locale.library

   - Supports up to @{fg shine}9 @{"accounts" LINK "Comptes"} at the same time@{fg text} .

   - Plays requested module (Pro/Noise/SoundTracker format).

   - Offers a great choice of@{fg shine} @{"Preferences" LINK "Préférences"}@{fg text} like @{fg shine}screenmode@{fg text}, @{fg shine}credits color choice@{fg text},
     @{fg shine}debits@{fg text}, @{fg shine}predefined operations@{fg text}, palette choice...
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Bugs" "Bugs"
@TOC "MAIN"
