  I was pointed out that BlitzBank crashed on A600 and A3000. Since version 2.30, Blitzbank is compiled
  with the last version of BLitz compiler. It corrects lots of bugs, especially with gadtool. I hope
  that this version will work on Amiga with 68000 and on A3000. If you made tests, please write to me.

  If you notice another bug, you would be kind to write to :

                    Thibault Richard
                    87,rue Emile Paladilhe
                    93150 Le Blanc-Mesnil
                    mail: thibault@brest.univ-paris13.fr

  N.B.1: If you have smashing ideas to improve BlitzBank, write to me and I'll see if I can include
         them in the program.
