  BlitzBank is SHAREWARE. To register, send 100 FF or 15 Ł or 30 DM or 20 dollars to

                    THIBAULT Richard
                    87,rue Emile Paladilhe
                    93150 Le Blanc-Menil
                    (check to the order of Thibault Richard)
                    (don't forget your adress if it's different from the one on the check !!)
                    (I also accept international money order)

   You will receive a keyfile to put in Blitzbank's directory that helps the program to recognize
   you as a register user.
   If you later want to obtain a newer version, you'll just have to search for it
